# Neurex Tech Stack

Authoritative dependency map from root and workspace `package.json` files, plus registry-declared consumer dependencies. Do not add packages outside the correct layer.

Related: `project-directory-structure.mdc`, `docs/STYLE.md`, `docs/TOKENS.md`, `AGENTS.md`.

